. Supplier Dataset

Captures supplier reliability and delivery performance.

Field	Type	Description

supplier_id	String	Unique supplier identifier
supplier_name	String	Supplier name
material_id	String	Material supplied
avg_lead_time_days	Integer	Historical average lead time
on_time_delivery_rate	Float	% of deliveries made on time
current_delay_flag	Boolean	Whether supplier has active delay
delay_reason	String	Text describing disruption cause
reliability_score	Float	Composite score (0–1)



---

B. Procurement Dataset

Holds purchase orders, material demands, and sourcing options.

Field	Type	Description

po_id	String	Purchase order identifier
material_id	String	Material ordered
supplier_id	String	Linked supplier
order_date	Date	Date of order
expected_delivery_date	Date	Planned delivery date
quantity_ordered	Float	Units ordered
unit_price	Float	Cost per unit
expedite_option	Boolean	Can order be expedited?
alternate_supplier_ids	Array[String]	List of backup suppliers



---

C. Logistics Dataset

Represents shipment tracking, routing, and delay events.

Field	Type	Description

shipment_id	String	Shipment identifier
po_id	String	Linked purchase order
origin	String	Supplier location
destination	String	Plant location
route_id	String	Assigned route
carrier_id	String	Transport provider
status	String	e.g., In Transit, Delayed, Delivered
estimated_arrival	DateTime	Predicted arrival
delay_reason	String	Cause of delay
reroute_possible	Boolean	Can be re-routed



---

D. Production Dataset

Tracks material consumption and production priorities.

Field	Type	Description

plant_id	String	Manufacturing plant
material_id	String	Material used
inventory_level	Float	Current stock
daily_consumption_rate	Float	Usage per day
criticality_score	Float	Impact on production (0–1)
current_status	String	e.g., Running, Paused, Low Material